<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-06-16T06:30:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-06-16T06:30:00-05:00" n="343" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d343">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">795.00/6–1651: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in India</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Steere</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left">
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                            </seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">New Delhi</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-06-16T17:00:00+05:30">June 16,
                                    1951—5 p. m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>3661. <gloss target="#t_Embtel1">Embtel</gloss> 3567 June 9. Bajpai has
                            asked whether Emb had recd info re US position in which <gloss target="#t_GOI1">GOI</gloss> interested for purpose transmission
                            Panikkar. I replied in negative.</p>
                        <p>In absence response I will assume Dept not interested providing special
                            statement this character. Bajpai incidentally left Delhi today on 6 week
                            holiday.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Steere</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>